    "With SMOTE the recall increased tremendously however it labels Normal Traffic as attacks. For information security it is more important to distuingish the actual attacks more accurately even when precision and overall accuracy decreases. The macro f1-score was still low but with SMOTE it increased to 0.438 (43,8%) which makes this model more valuable.\n",
