   "source": [
    "In the code snippet for Logistic Regression the dimensionality reduction (pca__n_components) was tested with values 4, 6, 8 and 10 to find the optimal balance.\n",
    "\n",
    "The Regularization Strength (clf__C) was explored with values (10.0, 50.0, 100.0). These higher values indicate a preference for less regularization to allow the model to fit the training data more closely. In initial testing the values were 1.0, 5.0 and 10.0. GridSearchCV selected the maximum values from the range (10.0) so to find the true optimum, the grid was expanded to higher values to prevent artificial limiting of the model's potential.\n",
    "\n",
    "The max_iter=2000 was set for model stability and to ensure that the solver had enough iterations to converge."
